      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer la dérivée $n$-ième de $\\frac{1}{X^2+1}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer la dérivée <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>-ième de\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{X^2+1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ee137f73-82eb-4594-b25d-92a956314a7d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $n\\in\\Nn^*$. $\\frac{1}{X^2+1}=\\frac{1}{2i}(\\frac{1}{X-i}-\\frac{1}{X+i})$. Donc,\n\n$$\\begin{align*}\\ensuremath\n\\left(\\frac{1}{X^2+1}\\right)^{(n)}&=\\frac{1}{2i}(\\left(\\frac{1}{X-i}\\right)^{(n)}-\\left(\\frac{1}{X+i}\\right)^{(n)})=\\frac{1}{2i}(\\frac{(-1)(-2)...(-n)}{(X-i)^{n+1}}-\\frac{(-1)(-2)...(-n)}{(X+i)^{n+1}})\\\\\n &=(-1)^n.n!\\mbox{Im}(\\frac{1}{(X-i)^{n+1}})=(-1)^n.n!\\mbox{Im}(\\frac{(X+i)^{n+1}}{(X^2+1)^{n+1}})\n=\\frac{(-1)^n.n!\\sum_{}^{}C_{n+1}^{2k+1}(-1)^kX^{2n-2k}}{(X^2+1)^{n+1}}\n\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\in\\Nn^*\\)</span>. <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{X^2+1}=\\frac{1}{2i}(\\frac{1}{X-i}-\\frac{1}{X+i})\\)</span>.\nDonc,</p>\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\\ensuremath\n\\left(\\frac{1}{X^2+1}\\right)^{(n)}&amp;=\\frac{1}{2i}(\\left(\\frac{1}{X-i}\\right)^{(n)}-\\left(\\frac{1}{X+i}\\right)^{(n)})=\\frac{1}{2i}(\\frac{(-1)(-2)...(-n)}{(X-i)^{n+1}}-\\frac{(-1)(-2)...(-n)}{(X+i)^{n+1}})\\\\\n&amp;=(-1)^n.n!\\mbox{Im}(\\frac{1}{(X-i)^{n+1}})=(-1)^n.n!\\mbox{Im}(\\frac{(X+i)^{n+1}}{(X^2+1)^{n+1}})\n=\\frac{(-1)^n.n!\\sum_{}^{}C_{n+1}^{2k+1}(-1)^kX^{2n-2k}}{(X^2+1)^{n+1}}\n\\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
